snippet.title: Stage at the opening performance of the ADB Annual Meeting held in korea.
snippet.description:
Hello! This is JennyğŸ˜„

last May,
Asian Development Bank (ADB) annual meeting held in Songdo for the first time in three years
I went to the opening ceremony!!

Many people requested to see the full performance video, so I uploaded it on YouTube.

President Yoon Seok-yeol & Finance Ministers from 68 Asian Countries & Presidents of National Banks I played in front of VIPs, but the stage was big and it was a national event, so I was nervous.
Fortunately, I finished it safely without any mistakes ^^

I played for 3 out of 10 minutes of the opening ceremony.
I played the part of difficult and difficult times with Corona.
Of all the stages I've been on, I think this is the stage where the audience had the most money (?) LOLğŸ¤£

On Friday, I'll come back with a behind-the-scenes vlog of this performance^^

If you are curious about the full video of the opening performance, go to the link below and watch it!
Full video of opening performance ğŸ‘‰ https://youtu.be/H7XRoj5-iz4

snippet.title: [1hour] 'Raffine Gold' Coffee Music | Jenny Yun X Relativity Coffee
snippet.description:
New album 'Raffine Gold' was released!
It's collaboration Project with Jenny Yun X Relativity Coffee
You can enjoy Drip coffee with Jenny's Music!!


Raffine Gold
(Elegant, colorful, but soft and dignified inside)

01. Classic Coffee
02. Gold Coffee

______________________________

Jenny Yun X Relativity Coffee

Get drunk on coffee and fall in love with music!

Through a special collaboration project between Jenny Yun and Relativity Coffee, 
There are 6 kinds of drip coffee and 6 kinds of delicious music
It was released with the launch of coffee.

As if the coffee tastes different with whom and where
The taste of coffee seems to change depending on what kind of music you do with it.

This project was done with 7 composers who came to mind 
It is a song composed by the inspiration of coffee taste.

With this album and relativity, we're going to have a drip coffee time
I hope it will be a healing coffee time that makes you feel even better.

snippet.description:
New music 'Classic Coffee' was release.
thank you for watchingâœ¨ï¸âœ¨ï¸


Raffine Gold _  01.Classic Coffee 


:: Composer note ::

The languid afternoon air of the sun setting makes my heart flutter. 
We make hotter coffee in a hot coffee cup and wait for someone we don't know who it is in this place full of coffee scent. 
I try to get used to it, but I take a sip of coffee in a bitter mood, and the glass cools down like that.

Composed by ByeongKeun KIM
Piano by ByeongKeun KIM

Mastered by JJ

[Album Story]
We are experiencing a chaotic and embarrassing reality because of an unwelcome guest called "Covid 19."

Jenny Yun's second album "New Normal" is about finding happiness in our new daily lives.

We adapt well to all the new changes in our daily life.
I hope you find happiness with my second album, "New Normal."

Hello, It's Jenny.

Finally!
On June 22, my second album "New Normal" was released!! Hehe~~^^

I made a total of six films, and the first one is about the meeting between me and Jeddy, the pianist.
I hope you enjoy it. ^^* 
We'll be waiting for a lot of comments! Lol

The CD 2nd album will be sold in July and the music book will be sold in August.
We'll be back with our 2nd album showcase in July.

that sound is better than other $200 new Violin.

Anyway, personally, there were a lot of things I wanted to do,

snippet.title: HAVANA Dance-Violin Cover (Busan,Ulsan Haeparang Trail) | Jenny Yun
snippet.description:
Hi everyone!
I'm Jenny Yun, the Dance-olinist.
You might already know if you've seen my videos before, but let me explain this again just in case.
Dance-olin is a combination of Dance and Violin, which refers to playing the violin while dancing.
 
Today, I played a pop song for the first time with dancing-olin.
This means a lot to me since I've created my own choreography and put a lot of effort into it.

Havana, ooh na-na ~~
Y'all know this famous song right?
Please enjoy!

The special thing about this video is that I filmed this video in Busan and Ulsan Haeparang Trail, which was an AMAZING experience.
The video turned out to be fantastic thanks to the beautiful backdrop!

I am always thankful to all of you for your support. :)
There are many other beautiful cities apart from Seoul!

Visit Korea~!
Thank you!!

snippet.description:
Big Bang is back with a song 'Still Life.'

BIGBANG is an idol who set a new era
It's the history of K-pop
They are artist who was with me when I was a student.

I knew that I had a lot of memories about Big Bang songs.
When I first listened to this new song, it reminded me of my childhood and songs
It's so nice to see you all of a sudden.  It reminds me of the hard times.
You know when you get choked up and cry?

Even if you listen to it again, the lyrics, voice, instrumental sounds, chorus, and melody 
It was so perfect.
It's like you're cheering for us not to give up no matter how hard it is 
I think this song is more meaningful.
Each and every member voice is so precious...

Thank you for releasing this album. Big Bang oppa ğŸ’•ğŸ’•
Please continue to release album.
It's an honor to cover it.^^

I filmed this video on the rooftop of a building in Seoul.
The wind was so strong.
It was cold, hard, hungry, and almost flew away
I prepared this video thinking about my subscribers who will watch my video. 
Please watch it often and spread about my channel!ğŸ˜Š
